SELECT t."Key", t."Id", t."Code", t."CreatedAt", t."Description", t."Group", t."IsActive", t."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedAt", p."Description", p."Group", p."IsActive", p."Name", COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p
    WHERE p."IsActive"
) AS t
ORDER BY t."Key"

FROM "Plans" AS p
LEFT JOIN "PlanPermissions" AS p0 ON p."Id" = p0."PlanId"

ORDER BY p."Id"

SELECT t."Key", t."Id", t."Code", t."CreatedAt", t."Description", t."Group", t."IsActive", t."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedAt", p."Description", p."Group", p."IsActive", p."Name", COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p
    WHERE p."IsActive"
) AS t
ORDER BY t."Key"

SELECT t."Key", t."Id", t."Code", t."CreatedAt", t."Description", t."Group", t."IsActive", t."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Code", p."CreatedAt", p."Description", p."Group", p."IsActive", p."Name", COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p
    WHERE p."IsActive"
) AS t
ORDER BY t."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

) AS t0

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

2025-08-15 19:38:04.124 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

2025-08-15 21:03:31.097 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

FROM "Plans" AS p

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

2025-08-15 21:53:30.268 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

    FROM (

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"

2025-08-15 23:10:41.611 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t0."Key", t1."Id", t1."Code", t1."CreatedAt", t1."Description", t1."Group", t1."IsActive", t1."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Key"
    FROM (
        SELECT COALESCE(p."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
        FROM "Permissions" AS p
        WHERE p."IsActive"
    ) AS t
    GROUP BY t."Key"
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."Id", p0."Code", p0."CreatedAt", p0."Description", p0."Group", p0."IsActive", p0."Name", COALESCE(p0."Group", 'Ungrouped') AS "Key"
    FROM "Permissions" AS p0
    WHERE p0."IsActive"
) AS t1 ON t0."Key" = t1."Key"
ORDER BY t0."Key"
